<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">
                <h1>槟城旅游</h1>
            </div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#tourist-spots">旅游景点</a></li>
                <li><a href="#food">美食佳肴</a></li>
                <li><a href="#hotels">住宿酒店</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>欢迎来到槟城</h1>
                <p>探索东方明珠</p>
                <a href="#explore" class="hero-btn">开始探索</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="tourist-spots" class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">热门景点</h2>
            <div class="spots-grid">
                <div class="spot-card">
                    <img src="/images/georgetown.jpg" alt="乔治市古迹">
                    <h3>乔治市古迹</h3>
                    <p>联合国教科文组织世界文化遗产，独特的建筑和文化风貌</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">了解更多</a>
                </div>
                <div class="spot-card">
                    <img src="/images/kek-lok-si.jpg" alt="极乐寺">
                    <h3>极乐寺</h3>
                    <p>马来西亚最大的佛教寺庙，建筑宏伟壮观</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">了解更多</a>
                </div>
                <div class="spot-card">
                    <img src="/images/penang-hill.jpg" alt="槟城山">
                    <h3>槟城山</h3>
                    <p>历史悠久的缆车铁路，俯瞰城市美景</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">了解更多</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="food" class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">地道美食</h2>
            <div class="food-grid">
                <div class="food-card">
                    <img src="/images/char-kuey-teow.jpg" alt="炒粿条">
                    <h3>槟城炒粿条</h3>
                    <p>槟城最著名的炒面，香气四溢</p>
                </div>
                <div class="food-card">
                    <img src="/images/asam-laksa.jpg" alt="亚参叻沙">
                    <h3>亚参叻沙</h3>
                    <p>酸辣开胃的鱼汤面，独特风味</p>
                </div>
                <div class="food-card">
                    <img src="/images/nasi-kandar.jpg" alt="椰浆饭">
                    <h3>娘惹椰浆饭</h3>
                    <p>多种咖喱配搭的米饭，风味十足</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="hotels" class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">住宿推荐</h2>
            <div class="hotel-grid">
                <div class="hotel-card">
                    <img src="/images/luxury-hotel.jpg" alt="豪华酒店">
                    <h3>豪华酒店</h3>
                    <p>体验世界级的住宿服务</p>
                    <ul class="hotel-features">
                        <li>东方文华酒店</li>
                        <li>香格里拉沙洋度假村</li>
                        <li>槟城皇家酒店</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="hotel-card">
                    <img src="/images/boutique-hotel.jpg" alt="精品酒店">
                    <h3>特色精品酒店</h3>
                    <p>入住经典修复的历史建筑</p>
                    <ul class="hotel-features">
                        <li>七间房精品酒店</li>
                        <li>张弼士故居</li>
                        <li>爱巷23号</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="hotel-card">
                    <img src="/images/budget-hotel.jpg" alt="经济型酒店">
                    <h3>经济实惠选择</h3>
                    <p>舒适便利的平价住宿</p>
                    <ul class="hotel-features">
                        <li>亚美尼亚街传统酒店</li>
                        <li>B街酒店</li>
                        <li>集装箱主题酒店</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>联系我们</h3>
                <p>邮箱: info@visitpenang.com</p>
                <p>电话: +604 123 4567</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>关注我们</h3>
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="#">微信</a>
                    <a href="#">微博</a>
                    <a href="#">小红书</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>快速链接</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#tourist-spots">旅游景点</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#food">美食佳肴</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#hotels">住宿酒店</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; 2024 槟城旅游. 版权所有.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/javascripts/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 